            [Content to Be Added]
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- High School Writings Section -->
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-8" style="color: var(--color-text);">High School Writings</h2>
          <p class="text-lg" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
            I used to write a lot when I was in high school. I still think some of them were pretty good. Trigger warning: one of them contains a lot of gore. (<a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1PtqCmPduUj8gmmW_rmlmOfFBih0bU9wX?usp=sharing" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-link);">link</a>)
